{{refimprove|date=June 2013}}
'''Woodstock Roller Derby''' (WRD) is a women's flat-track [[roller derby]] league located in [[Woodstock, Ontario]]. WRD was started in 2011 and currently has one team called The Woodstock Warriors. The league's first public event was held in September 2012, against the Rollergettes from [[Toronto]].<ref name=debut>{{cite news|last=Thomson|first=Ron|title=Roller derby makes Woodstock debut|url=http://www.woodstocksentinelreview.com/2012/09/23/roller-derby-makes-woodstock-debut|accessdate=4 June 2013|newspaper=Woodstock Sentinel Review|date=23 September 2012}}</ref>

